description: Lists geofence collections in your Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: An optional limit for the number of resources returned in a single call. Default value: 100

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token specifying which page of results to return in the response. If no token is provided, the default page is the first page. Default value: null.

nested_items.name: UpdateTime
